data.description: Stunning is the word that best describes this house, and the huge lot it sits on. This one-owner home was the model for the  neighborhood so has all of the upgrades, plus additional upgrades added in the last couple of years. Home features a screened  and tiled porch with amazing water views, custom mantle and backsplash, stunning tile in the downstairs bathroom, new  hardwood on the stairs, and so much more! Come see the beautiful hardwood floors, walk-in pantry, large master with sitting  room, and master bath with oversized shower and separate tub. See why River Bluff is such a high-demand neighborhood, and  why this house is a true gem. Plus, deep water access with no flood insurance! Assumable VA loan at 3.25%!!!
